name: Corbins of the Rose-Covered Tram
description: Hailing from the Rootmason capital city of Thespin, the Corbins of the Rose-Covered Tram Are known for their love, romance, joy and great luck. Now serving as caretakers of Mohoan Larvae, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
